Use the standard library
This is how to even_odd_count of num:
   Remember that n is abs of num
   Remember that evens is 0
   Remember that odds is 0

   When n is 0, then:
      Increase evens
      The answer is [evens, odds]
   End when

   Do this n times:
      When n is 0, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when

      Remember that digit is remainder of n and 10
      Remember that check is remainder of digit and 2

      When check is 0, then:
         Increase evens
      But, if not:
         Increase odds
      End when

      Remember that n is quotient of n and 10
   End do

   The answer is [evens, odds]
Now you know